      "seed": 186699714,
      "versionNonce": 1499633040,
      "text": "•  /welcome  → invitation acceptance UI (OrgInvitationTable)\n•  /{tenantSlug}/admin/staff  → invite + list + withdraw UI\n•  Kundencenter auto-join  (/welcome?code=…  → /org-setup)\n•  Calls account-be at account/users/tenant-invitations,\n    account/tenants/{tid}/invitations/{id}/{accept,decline}\n•  Hub-be: scaffolding only — Program.cs has\n    “// ToDo: add the modules here” — defers to account-be",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "•  /welcome  → invitation acceptance UI (OrgInvitationTable)\n•  /{tenantSlug}/admin/staff  → invite + list + withdraw UI\n•  Kundencenter auto-join  (/welcome?code=…  → /org-setup)\n•  Calls account-be at account/users/tenant-invitations,\n    account/tenants/{tid}/invitations/{id}/{accept,decline}\n•  Hub-be: scaffolding only — Program.cs has\n    “// ToDo: add the modules here” — defers to account-be",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
