      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "seed": 986607412,
      "versionNonce": 2089860496,
      "text": "Frontend (account-fe):\n  •  NEW  src/routes/_common/invite.tsx   ?token=…\n  •  NEW  src/modules/invitation/  (preview + accept/decline UI)\n  •  Threads return_to through Ory login & registration flows\n\nBackend (account-be):\n  •  NEW  GET   invitations/verify?token=…   (anonymous-allowed)\n  •  NEW  POST  invitations/accept   { token }   (bearer; email-bound)\n  •  NEW  POST  tenants/{tid}/invitations/{id}/resend   (rate-limited)\n  •  TenantInvitation gets: TokenHash, ExpiresAt, AcceptedAt,\n        RevokedAt, ResendCount, LastResentAt\n  •  Aux Cosmos doc tenantinvitationtokens (id=tokenHash, TTL)\n  •  LinkService → '{AccountServiceBaseUrl}/invite?token=…'\n  •  Accept handler: requestContext.UserEmail == invitation.Email\n        AND Ory VerifiableAddress.verified == true",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Frontend (account-fe):\n  •  NEW  src/routes/_common/invite.tsx   ?token=…\n  •  NEW  src/modules/invitation/  (preview + accept/decline UI)\n  •  Threads return_to through Ory login & registration flows\n\nBackend (account-be):\n  •  NEW  GET   invitations/verify?token=…   (anonymous-allowed)\n  •  NEW  POST  invitations/accept   { token }   (bearer; email-bound)\n  •  NEW  POST  tenants/{tid}/invitations/{id}/resend   (rate-limited)\n  •  TenantInvitation gets: TokenHash, ExpiresAt, AcceptedAt,\n        RevokedAt, ResendCount, LastResentAt\n  •  Aux Cosmos doc tenantinvitationtokens (id=tokenHash, TTL)\n  •  LinkService → '{AccountServiceBaseUrl}/invite?token=…'\n  •  Accept handler: requestContext.UserEmail == invitation.Email\n        AND Ory VerifiableAddress.verified == true",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "aV",
      "autoResize": true
    },
