      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "seed": 812896394,
      "versionNonce": 616729488,
      "text": "1.  256-bit token, sha256-hashed at rest, single-use, 7-day TTL\n2.  Claims-email must match invitation.Email  (constant-time compare)\n3.  Email must be Ory-verified before membership write\n4.  ETag concurrency on TenantInvitation update — no double-accept\n5.  Rate-limit: invite, resend, verify (per inviter / invitation / IP)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1.  256-bit token, sha256-hashed at rest, single-use, 7-day TTL\n2.  Claims-email must match invitation.Email  (constant-time compare)\n3.  Email must be Ory-verified before membership write\n4.  ETag concurrency on TenantInvitation update — no double-accept\n5.  Rate-limit: invite, resend, verify (per inviter / invitation / IP)",
