      "seed": 605066990,
      "versionNonce": 1095585680,
      "text": "id              string    (Cosmos doc id — NEVER in URL anymore)\ntenantId        string    PartitionKey\nemail           string    lowercased; used for accept match\ninputEmail      string    original casing for display\ninvitedBy       string    inviter userId\nroleId          string    role to assign on accept\nstatus          enum      New | Accepted | Declined | Withdrawn | Revoked\ninvitedAt       datetime\n\n── NEW FIELDS ─────────────────────────────────\ntokenHash       string?   sha256(token), hex; nulled after accept\nexpiresAt       datetime  default invitedAt + 7d\nacceptedAt      datetime?\nrevokedAt       datetime?\nresendCount     int       cap 5 / 24h\nlastResentAt    datetime?",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
