      "seed": 1476388842,
      "versionNonce": 987071344,
      "text": "Purpose:  O(1) token-to-invitation lookup at /invitations/verify\n          without cross-partition scan on tenantinvitations.\n\nid              string    tokenHash         (== document id)\npartitionKey    string    tokenHash[0..2]   (or full hash)\ninvitationId    string\ntenantId        string\nexpiresAt       datetime\nttl             int       seconds-until-expiresAt — Cosmos\n                          auto-deletes expired tokens\n\nWrites:  CreateTenantInvitationCommand + ResendCommand\nReads:   VerifyInvitationTokenQuery\nDeletes: TTL auto + AcceptInvitationByTokenHandler",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Purpose:  O(1) token-to-invitation lookup at /invitations/verify\n          without cross-partition scan on tenantinvitations.\n\nid              string    tokenHash         (== document id)\npartitionKey    string    tokenHash[0..2]   (or full hash)\ninvitationId    string\ntenantId        string\nexpiresAt       datetime\nttl             int       seconds-until-expiresAt — Cosmos\n                          auto-deletes expired tokens\n\nWrites:  CreateTenantInvitationCommand + ResendCommand\nReads:   VerifyInvitationTokenQuery\nDeletes: TTL auto + AcceptInvitationByTokenHandler",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b3E",
      "autoResize": true
    },
