      "versionNonce": 1173161769,
      "text": "•  Ory-fronted login / signup / verification / MFA / recovery\n•  TenantInvitation aggregate  (Cosmos: tenantinvitations,\n    pk=tenantId)  — Status: New|Accepted|Declined|Withdrawn|Revoked\n•  Endpoints (FastEndpoints + Wemogy CQRS):\n      POST  tenants/{tid}/members/invite\n      POST  tenants/{tid}/invitations/{id}/accept   ← bearer required\n      POST  …/decline   …/withdraw   …/remove\n      GET   users/tenant-invitations   ← matches by claims.email\n      GET   tenants/{tid}/invitations/sent\n•  LinkService.GetInvitationLink()  ⇒  '{HubBaseUrl}/welcome'\n    (hardcoded, NO token, NO invitationId, same link for everyone)\n•  Sends Sendgrid template d-3a5d4401cd064c0a929cc74f61cb507a",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "•  Ory-fronted login / signup / verification / MFA / recovery\n•  TenantInvitation aggregate  (Cosmos: tenantinvitations,\n    pk=tenantId)  — Status: New|Accepted|Declined|Withdrawn|Revoked\n•  Endpoints (FastEndpoints + Wemogy CQRS):\n      POST  tenants/{tid}/members/invite\n      POST  tenants/{tid}/invitations/{id}/accept   ← bearer required\n      POST  …/decline   …/withdraw   …/remove\n      GET   users/tenant-invitations   ← matches by claims.email\n      GET   tenants/{tid}/invitations/sent\n•  LinkService.GetInvitationLink()  ⇒  '{HubBaseUrl}/welcome'\n    (hardcoded, NO token, NO invitationId, same link for everyone)\n•  Sends Sendgrid template d-3a5d4401cd064c0a929cc74f61cb507a",
