      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1.  256-bit token, sha256-hashed at rest, single-use, 7-day TTL\n2.  Claims-email must match invitation.Email  (constant-time compare)\n3.  Email must be Ory-verified before membership write\n4.  ETag concurrency on TenantInvitation update — no double-accept\n5.  Rate-limit: invite, resend, verify (per inviter / invitation / IP)",
