      "versionNonce": 398603977,
      "text": "Two parallel invitee surfaces, one domain:\n  •  account/invite?token=…  (email link)\n  •  hub/welcome  (in-app, by claims.email)\nBoth call account-be commands; both produce\nthe same TenantMember write + Permit.io sync.\nServer-side guards make both safe.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
