      "index": "b93",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "YtEt_MdYcKXh-MMcwhTiX"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1779969559602,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "version": 188,
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "id": "FhHDqa1xQqwG36dxzcRtY",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3774.0862234836445,
      "y": 5444.648516374881,
      "width": 922.4,
      "height": 289,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "seed": 1649838119,
      "versionNonce": 1981666281,
      "text": "Step                                                                Enforced where\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n1.  Hash incoming token; lookup by tokenHash                        VerifyInvitationToken / AcceptInvitationByToken handlers\n2.  Reject if expiresAt < now()                                     handler — returns 410 Gone\n3.  Reject if status != New                                         handler — single-use enforced (tokenHash nulled on accept)\n4.  Bearer present & valid Ory session                              JTL.Platform.Internal.Dotnet.Host auth middleware\n5.  requestContext.UserEmail == invitation.Email   (case-insens.)   AcceptInvitationByTokenCommandAuthorization (constant-time)\n6.  Ory VerifiableAddress[invitation.Email].verified == true        handler — GetIdentityQuery into Identity module\n7.  Mark Accepted + null TokenHash + add TenantMember               single Cosmos transactional batch (ETag concurrency)\n8.  Permit.io sync                                                  AcceptInvitationByTokenCommandPostProcessor\n9.  Audit event {invitationId, userId, ip, ua, at}                  PostProcessor / structured log\n\nRate-limits (FastEndpoints throttle, distributed via existing infrastructure):\n  •  POST  members/invite       — 100 / inviter / hour\n  •  POST  invitations/{id}/resend  — 1 / min, 5 / 24h\n  •  GET   invitations/verify   — 20 / ip / min  (open enumeration shield)\n\nOpen-redirect: account-fe validates Ory return_to against allowlist\n  {jtlAccountServiceUrl, jtlHubUrl, jtlPartnerPortalUrl, jtlAppStoreUrl}",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Step                                                                Enforced where\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n1.  Hash incoming token; lookup by tokenHash                        VerifyInvitationToken / AcceptInvitationByToken handlers\n2.  Reject if expiresAt < now()                                     handler — returns 410 Gone\n3.  Reject if status != New                                         handler — single-use enforced (tokenHash nulled on accept)\n4.  Bearer present & valid Ory session                              JTL.Platform.Internal.Dotnet.Host auth middleware\n5.  requestContext.UserEmail == invitation.Email   (case-insens.)   AcceptInvitationByTokenCommandAuthorization (constant-time)\n6.  Ory VerifiableAddress[invitation.Email].verified == true        handler — GetIdentityQuery into Identity module\n7.  Mark Accepted + null TokenHash + add TenantMember               single Cosmos transactional batch (ETag concurrency)\n8.  Permit.io sync                                                  AcceptInvitationByTokenCommandPostProcessor\n9.  Audit event {invitationId, userId, ip, ua, at}                  PostProcessor / structured log\n\nRate-limits (FastEndpoints throttle, distributed via existing infrastructure):\n  •  POST  members/invite       — 100 / inviter / hour\n  •  POST  invitations/{id}/resend  — 1 / min, 5 / 24h\n  •  GET   invitations/verify   — 20 / ip / min  (open enumeration shield)\n\nOpen-redirect: account-fe validates Ory return_to against allowlist\n  {jtlAccountServiceUrl, jtlHubUrl, jtlPartnerPortalUrl, jtlAppStoreUrl}",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b94",
      "autoResize": true
    },
