      "seed": 805199728,
      "versionNonce": 1393436560,
      "text": "•  OrgInvitationTable still rendered\n•  useUserTenantInvitationsQuery   (unchanged)\n•  useAcceptInvitationCommand      (unchanged)\n•  useDeclineInvitationCommand     (unchanged)\n•  Email link target still:\n       {HubBaseUrl}/welcome   (hardcoded; same for everyone)\n•  Same Ory-login bounce via beforeLoadAuthenticated\n•  Same staff/admin page (send / list / withdraw)\n\nInvitee with NO Ory account yet → Ory's login\nscreen shows a 'Sign up' link, user enters\nregistration flow there; bounces back when done.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "•  OrgInvitationTable still rendered\n•  useUserTenantInvitationsQuery   (unchanged)\n•  useAcceptInvitationCommand      (unchanged)\n•  useDeclineInvitationCommand     (unchanged)\n•  Email link target still:\n       {HubBaseUrl}/welcome   (hardcoded; same for everyone)\n•  Same Ory-login bounce via beforeLoadAuthenticated\n•  Same staff/admin page (send / list / withdraw)\n\nInvitee with NO Ory account yet → Ory's login\nscreen shows a 'Sign up' link, user enters\nregistration flow there; bounces back when done.",
