      "height": 124,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "seed": 577813872,
      "versionNonce": 526757744,
      "text": "•  OrgInvitationTable still rendered\n•  useUserTenantInvitationsQuery / Suspense   (unchanged)\n•  useAcceptInvitationCommand                 (unchanged)\n•  useDeclineInvitationCommand                (unchanged)\n•  Email link target still:\n       {HubBaseUrl}/welcome   (hardcoded; no token)\n•  Same Ory-login bounce via beforeLoadAuthenticated\n",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "•  OrgInvitationTable still rendered\n•  useUserTenantInvitationsQuery / Suspense   (unchanged)\n•  useAcceptInvitationCommand                 (unchanged)\n•  useDeclineInvitationCommand                (unchanged)\n•  Email link target still:\n       {HubBaseUrl}/welcome   (hardcoded; no token)\n•  Same Ory-login bounce via beforeLoadAuthenticated\n",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "index": "bEP",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "RVjUKpF3RYCVUbzb-p_nh"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1780031574892,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "version": 86,
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "id": "oT3LGSauB-vAzftXOtxG7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -13.944403468101882,
      "y": -366.92631446403266,
      "width": 677.6,
      "height": 154,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "seed": 844599152,
      "versionNonce": 1742618992,
      "text": "How each invitee state is handled:\n\n  State 1  (already logged in):\n    /welcome lists all New invitations matching claims.email and offers Accept.\n\n  State 2  (has account, logged out):\n    beforeLoadAuthenticated bounces to Ory login; back to /welcome with session.\n\n  State 3  (no Ory account yet):\n    Ory's login page exposes 'Sign up' → registration + verification mail → back to /welcome.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "How each invitee state is handled:\n\n  State 1  (already logged in):\n    /welcome lists all New invitations matching claims.email and offers Accept.\n\n  State 2  (has account, logged out):\n    beforeLoadAuthenticated bounces to Ory login; back to /welcome with session.\n\n  State 3  (no Ory account yet):\n    Ory's login page exposes 'Sign up' → registration + verification mail → back to /welcome.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "index": "bEQ",
      "autoResize": true
    },
