      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "seed": 1915651440,
      "versionNonce": 1008367472,
      "text": "POST  tenants/{tid}/invitations/{id}/accept\nPOST  tenants/{tid}/invitations/{id}/decline\n──────────────────────────────────────────\n+  NEW GUARD  (constant-time string compare):\n      if (!string.Equals(invitation.Email,\n                         requestContext.UserEmail,\n                         StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase))\n          throw Error.Forbidden(InvitationEmailMismatch);\n\nNo schema migration.  No new endpoints.\nNo LinkService change.\nNo token, no expiry, no single-use semantics.\n\nDiscovery still happens via\n  GET /users/tenant-invitations  filtered by claims.email\nso users who are logged in as the WRONG account simply\nsee an empty list — the guard never fires for them.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "POST  tenants/{tid}/invitations/{id}/accept\nPOST  tenants/{tid}/invitations/{id}/decline\n──────────────────────────────────────────\n+  NEW GUARD  (constant-time string compare):\n      if (!string.Equals(invitation.Email,\n                         requestContext.UserEmail,\n                         StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase))\n          throw Error.Forbidden(InvitationEmailMismatch);\n\nNo schema migration.  No new endpoints.\nNo LinkService change.\nNo token, no expiry, no single-use semantics.\n\nDiscovery still happens via\n  GET /users/tenant-invitations  filtered by claims.email\nso users who are logged in as the WRONG account simply\nsee an empty list — the guard never fires for them.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "index": "bET",
      "autoResize": true
    },
