      "id": "GRtdXfy5YT-W72AmBwkFH",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3464.7790766584276,
      "y": -466.81551856535793,
      "width": 353.59999999999997,
      "height": 199,
      "strokeColor": "#5c5f66",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "seed": 2056442768,
      "versionNonce": 62425456,
      "text": "No new route, no new module.\n\nUsers never see account.{env} as part of the\ninvitation acceptance journey except implicitly\nwhen Ory's bounce passes through the existing\n_anonymous/auth/registration & /verification\nroutes for State 3.\n\nWrong-account handling (State 1 mismatch) lives\nin hub-fe Welcome.tsx: it reads the verify\npreview, compares maskedEmail with claims.email,\nand renders a 'log out and sign in as …'\nmessage instead of the OrgInvitationTable.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "No new route, no new module.\n\nUsers never see account.{env} as part of the\ninvitation acceptance journey except implicitly\nwhen Ory's bounce passes through the existing\n_anonymous/auth/registration & /verification\nroutes for State 3.\n\nWrong-account handling (State 1 mismatch) lives\nin hub-fe Welcome.tsx: it reads the verify\npreview, compares maskedEmail with claims.email,\nand renders a 'log out and sign in as …'\nmessage instead of the OrgInvitationTable.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "index": "bI8",
      "autoResize": true
    },
