      "text": "NEW route:  src/routes/_common/invite.tsx\nNEW module: src/modules/invitation/\n  pages/Invitation.tsx\n  domain/queries/useVerifyInvitationQuery.ts\n  domain/commands/useAcceptInvitationCommand.ts\n  components/{InvitationPreviewCard,\n              InvitationExpiredState,\n              InvitationWrongEmailState}.tsx\n\n",
