      "seed": 1206980464,
      "versionNonce": 1094095216,
      "text": "How each invitee state is handled:\n\n  State 1  (already logged in):\n    /invite loader detects session, compares claims.email; match → preview + Accept; mismatch → InvitationWrongEmailState.\n\n  State 2  (has account, logged out):\n    /invite loader redirects to /_common/login with return_to=/invite?token=… and login_hint=invitedEmail.\n\n  State 3  (no Ory account yet):\n    /invite loader redirects to /_anonymous/auth/registration with email_hint + after_verification_return_to.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "How each invitee state is handled:\n\n  State 1  (already logged in):\n    /invite loader detects session, compares claims.email; match → preview + Accept; mismatch → InvitationWrongEmailState.\n\n  State 2  (has account, logged out):\n    /invite loader redirects to /_common/login with return_to=/invite?token=… and login_hint=invitedEmail.\n\n  State 3  (no Ory account yet):\n    /invite loader redirects to /_anonymous/auth/registration with email_hint + after_verification_return_to.",
