      "versionNonce": 1653917552,
      "text": "ROUTES (unchanged):\n  /_authenticated/welcome\n  /_authenticated/$tenantSlug/_appShellLayout/admin/staff\n\nSurface kept identically:\n  •  OrgInvitationTable shown post-login\n  •  useUserTenantInvitationsQuery / Suspense (kept)\n  •  useAcceptInvitationCommand   (kept)\n  •  useDeclineInvitationCommand  (kept)\n\nDriver: claims.email — server returns all\nStatus=New invitations where\n  Email == sessionUser.Email\n\n/welcome is the State-1 surface for users who\nskipped the email link (or have multiple pending\ninvites). Token-based /invite is the State-2 and\nState-3 entry point — they converge in account-be.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ROUTES (unchanged):\n  /_authenticated/welcome\n  /_authenticated/$tenantSlug/_appShellLayout/admin/staff\n\nSurface kept identically:\n  •  OrgInvitationTable shown post-login\n  •  useUserTenantInvitationsQuery / Suspense (kept)\n  •  useAcceptInvitationCommand   (kept)\n  •  useDeclineInvitationCommand  (kept)\n\nDriver: claims.email — server returns all\nStatus=New invitations where\n  Email == sessionUser.Email\n\n/welcome is the State-1 surface for users who\nskipped the email link (or have multiple pending\ninvites). Token-based /invite is the State-2 and\nState-3 entry point — they converge in account-be.",
