      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "id": "yir7s-fwJN9-q4-Ze5fp_",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5973.074720680211,
      "y": -538.1201116701397,
      "width": 418.4,
      "height": 319,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "seed": 1411038064,
      "versionNonce": 1339473264,
      "text": "Domain & infrastructure:\n  TenantInvitation += { TokenHash, ExpiresAt, AcceptedAt,\n      RevokedAt, ResendCount, LastResentAt }\n  Aux Cosmos doc tenantinvitationtokens (id=hash, TTL)\n  InvitationTokenGenerator (256-bit, sha256)\n  LinkService → {AccountServiceBaseUrl}/invite?token=…\n\nEndpoints:\n  GET   invitations/verify    (anonymous)        NEW\n  POST  invitations/accept    (token, bearer)    NEW\n  POST  tenants/{tid}/inv/{id}/resend            NEW\n  POST  tenants/{tid}/inv/{id}/accept            KEPT\n  POST  tenants/{tid}/inv/{id}/decline           KEPT\n  GET   users/tenant-invitations                  KEPT\n\nBOTH paths share domain effects:\n  1. claims.email == invitation.Email\n  2. Ory VerifiableAddress.verified == true\n  3. Status=Accepted ; TokenHash=null\n  4. Tenant.Members += {UserId, JoinedAt}\n  5. Permit.io sync ; audit log",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Domain & infrastructure:\n  TenantInvitation += { TokenHash, ExpiresAt, AcceptedAt,\n      RevokedAt, ResendCount, LastResentAt }\n  Aux Cosmos doc tenantinvitationtokens (id=hash, TTL)\n  InvitationTokenGenerator (256-bit, sha256)\n  LinkService → {AccountServiceBaseUrl}/invite?token=…\n\nEndpoints:\n  GET   invitations/verify    (anonymous)        NEW\n  POST  invitations/accept    (token, bearer)    NEW\n  POST  tenants/{tid}/inv/{id}/resend            NEW\n  POST  tenants/{tid}/inv/{id}/accept            KEPT\n  POST  tenants/{tid}/inv/{id}/decline           KEPT\n  GET   users/tenant-invitations                  KEPT\n\nBOTH paths share domain effects:\n  1. claims.email == invitation.Email\n  2. Ory VerifiableAddress.verified == true\n  3. Status=Accepted ; TokenHash=null\n  4. Tenant.Members += {UserId, JoinedAt}\n  5. Permit.io sync ; audit log",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "index": "bLk",
      "autoResize": true
    },
