      "text": "How each invitee state is handled:\n\n  State 1  (already logged in):\n    Same as C — preview + Accept on match, InvitationWrongEmailState on mismatch.\n\n  State 2  (has account, logged out):\n    Same as C — bounce to /_common/login with return_to.\n\n  State 3  (no Ory account yet):\n    Same as C — bounce to /_anonymous/auth/registration.",
