      "versionNonce": 693372784,
      "text": "REMOVED:\n  ✗  OrgInvitationTable\n  ✗  useUserTenantInvitationsQuery / Suspense\n  ✗  useAcceptInvitationCommand\n  ✗  useDeclineInvitationCommand\n  ✗  modules/organization/components/\n        org-invitation-table/  (entire folder)\n\nKEPT:\n  ✓  Kundencenter ?code= → /org-setup\n  ✓  JoinOrgAlert (no pending invites case)\n  ✓  OrgManualSetup\n\nPlus a 30-day legacy-email bridge that\nredirects pending-invite users out to\naccount.{env}/invitations — then removed.\n\nLogged-in users (State 1) who arrive at\n/welcome via old emails get bridged out to\naccount-fe /invite.",
