      "seed": 367887216,
      "versionNonce": 534642032,
      "text": "Endpoints marked [Obsolete] in Phase 2,\nREMOVED in Phase 3:\n\n  ✗  GET   account/users/tenant-invitations\n  ✗  POST  account/tenants/{tid}/inv/{id}/accept\n  ✗  POST  account/tenants/{tid}/inv/{id}/decline\n\nOnly the by-token equivalents survive:\n  ✓  GET   account/invitations/verify\n  ✓  POST  account/invitations/accept    { token }\n  ✓  POST  account/invitations/decline   { token }  (added)\n  ✓  Admin endpoints (sent / withdraw / resend)\n\nToken is the ONLY way to identify an\ninvitation from outside the database.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
