      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "seed": 2123954544,
      "versionNonce": 1021555568,
      "text": "Customer wants /welcome to keep its in-app invite list + accept/decline UI:\n  •  users who skip the email link still need a way to find pending invitations\n  •  multi-tenant users with several invites want triage in one place\n  •  the in-app surface is a recognizable UX entry point that support can point users to",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
