      "x": 9204.43661267644,
      "y": -510.81604589561675,
      "width": 346.4,
      "height": 259,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "seed": 1881260400,
      "versionNonce": 1195762032,
      "text": "Self-service flows used:\n  •  registration  → after_hooks → webhook\n  •  login         → after_hooks → webhook\n  •  verification  (standard email proof)\n  •  mfa           (standard challenge)\n\nEmail link points directly at Ory:\n  {OryUrl}/self-service/login/browser\n      ?return_to={AcctSvc}/invitations/finalize\n              ?invitation={tokenOrRef}\n      &email_hint=alice@example.com\n\nOry renders ALL UI pages the user sees\n(registration, email verification, MFA,\npassword recovery if needed).\n\n",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Self-service flows used:\n  •  registration  → after_hooks → webhook\n  •  login         → after_hooks → webhook\n  •  verification  (standard email proof)\n  •  mfa           (standard challenge)\n\nEmail link points directly at Ory:\n  {OryUrl}/self-service/login/browser\n      ?return_to={AcctSvc}/invitations/finalize\n              ?invitation={tokenOrRef}\n      &email_hint=alice@example.com\n\nOry renders ALL UI pages the user sees\n(registration, email verification, MFA,\npassword recovery if needed).\n\n",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "index": "bT5",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "XXcfZIanvzZ9SH4X5fbt1"
