      "seed": 265521040,
      "versionNonce": 1750806416,
      "text": "How each invitee state is handled:\n\n  State 1  (already logged in):\n    Server compares session.identity.email vs invitation.Email; match → just accept; mismatch → 409 + logout.\n\n  State 2  (has account, logged out):\n    Server: identity exists, no session → admin-API issue session, then accept.\n\n  State 3  (no Ory account yet):\n    Server: no identity → admin-API create identity + verify-email + issue session, then accept.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "How each invitee state is handled:\n\n  State 1  (already logged in):\n    Server compares session.identity.email vs invitation.Email; match → just accept; mismatch → 409 + logout.\n\n  State 2  (has account, logged out):\n    Server: identity exists, no session → admin-API issue session, then accept.\n\n  State 3  (no Ory account yet):\n    Server: no identity → admin-API create identity + verify-email + issue session, then accept.",
