      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "seed": 1393335184,
      "versionNonce": 464929680,
      "text": "•  Email-account compromise  →  tenant takeover. Today's flow has 'something you know' (Ory password +\n    optional MFA) as a second factor on top of the email; this flow removes that second factor.\n•  Hard to retrofit MFA into a magic-link path without re-introducing a password form (defeating the point).\n•  Compliance: passwordless B2B flows often require additional controls (device trust, IP allowlisting).",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "•  Email-account compromise  →  tenant takeover. Today's flow has 'something you know' (Ory password +\n    optional MFA) as a second factor on top of the email; this flow removes that second factor.\n•  Hard to retrofit MFA into a magic-link path without re-introducing a password form (defeating the point).\n•  Compliance: passwordless B2B flows often require additional controls (device trust, IP allowlisting).",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "index": "bWj",
      "autoResize": true
    },
